            <title>[HBASE-2829] Add ability for start/stop scripts to also run a hadoop/hdfs cluster</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2829</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are many new users of HBase who are not currently users of Hadoop.  To make it easier for these users to get started, we should add the ability for our scripts to optionally start/stop an HDFS cluster, just as we do for ZooKeeper.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
